# Repo-wide ignores. Module-specific ignores (build output, local.properties,
# etc.) live in android/.gitignore and web/.gitignore instead -- keep those
# concerns scoped to the module that generates them.

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# Editors. Anchored to the repo root (leading /) so this only covers the
# case of opening the whole monorepo as one IDE project -- android/.gitignore
# already handles android/.idea/ with its own, more selective rules (it
# deliberately keeps a few shared-config files tracked), and an unanchored
# pattern here would silently override that.
/.vscode/
/.idea/
*.swp
